term "Library" `The set of functions that define a DSL.
Run \`capy run lib.capy script.capy\` to apply it.`

term "Capture" `A typed slot in a function signature — e.g. a
\`string\` capture binds the next quoted argument.`

term "Verbatim block" `A body captured as raw bytes; blank lines
and \`#\` comment lines survive untouched.`
